(Requirements Document: Sweet Crumbs Bakery Cloud Storage Migration) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Document Type: Requirement Specification / Migration Requirements) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. DOCUMENT PURPOSE) Tj
T* (-------------------) Tj
T* (This document defines the detailed business, technical, security, migration, and testing) Tj
T* (requirements for Sweet Crumbs Bakery as it moves data from an on-premise server to a managed cloud) Tj
T* (storage platform.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The document is intended for internal planning, vendor evaluation, migration execution, and user) Tj
T* (acceptance testing.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. BUSINESS PROFILE AND CURRENT STATE) Tj
T* (-------------------------------------) Tj
T* (Sweet Crumbs Bakery operates one production kitchen, one retail storefront, and one small) Tj
T* (back-office location. The bakery currently stores all digital files on a single Windows-based file) Tj
T* (server located on site in the office.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The on-premise server holds approximately 1.8 TB of data and grows by an estimated 12 GB per) Tj
T* (month. There are 18 employees with some level of file access, including 4 staff members who need) Tj
T* (secure remote access.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Current protection relies on one nightly backup to a local NAS device. There is no active offsite) Tj
T* (redundancy, cloud replication, or ransomware-isolated backup copy.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (3. MIGRATION OBJECTIVES) Tj
T* (-----------------------) Tj
T* (The bakery requires a cloud storage solution that reduces dependence on a single physical server,) Tj
T* (supports secure access from bakery, office, and remote locations, and preserves all critical) Tj
T* (business records without loss or corruption.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The target solution must allow daily operations to continue during bakery business hours from) Tj
T* (05:00 to 20:00 local time with minimal disruption to production planning, supplier ordering,) Tj
T* (payroll processing, and financial reporting.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The migration must provide a controlled cutover with a tested rollback path and measurable) Tj
T* (validation of data completeness, permissions, and backup recoverability.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (4. IN-SCOPE DATA SETS) Tj
T* (---------------------) Tj
T* (In-scope content includes shared business documents, recipe files, production schedules, inventory) Tj
T* (spreadsheets, supplier contracts, supplier invoices, employee records, payroll support documents,) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
