(point-of-sale daily sales exports, financial reports, and backup archives from the last 7 years.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The existing folder hierarchy, naming structure, and ownership model must be preserved unless) Tj
T* (explicitly corrected during data cleanup.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Archived records older than 7 years may be moved into lower-cost archive storage if the retention) Tj
T* (and retrieval requirements in this document are met.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (5. OUT-OF-SCOPE ITEMS) Tj
T* (---------------------) Tj
T* (This effort does not include replacement of the bakery point-of-sale application, website hosting) Tj
T* (migration, email migration, ERP implementation, or redesign of bakery business processes.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Application modernization is out of scope unless directly required for file export, backup, or) Tj
T* (access continuity during the storage migration.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (6. BUSINESS REQUIREMENTS) Tj
T* (------------------------) Tj
T* (The bakery must be able to access active files from the storefront, kitchen office, and approved) Tj
T* (remote locations without dependence on the legacy on-premise server after cutover.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Authorized users must access the system through a familiar folder-style interface with minimal) Tj
T* (end-user training. Staff on the bakery floor must not be required to learn a complex document) Tj
T* (management workflow.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The migration must not exceed 2 hours of business-impacting downtime during final cutover. A) Tj
T* (weekend or after-hours cutover window is acceptable if the rollback procedure remains available) Tj
T* (until the system is signed off.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The solution must support secure external sharing of selected finance or audit documents with the) Tj
T* (bakery accountant without exposing internal employee or payroll records.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (7. FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS) Tj
T* (--------------------------) Tj
T* (The cloud storage environment must support at least 3 TB of data at go-live and scale to 5 TB) Tj
T* (without architecture changes or vendor migration.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The system must support the following file types at minimum: PDF, DOCX, XLSX, CSV, JPG, PNG, and) Tj
T* (ZIP backup files.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Folder structure and file names must be preserved during migration. Metadata that can be) Tj
T* (preserved, including last modified date and ownership mapping, should be retained where) Tj
T* (technically feasible.) Tj
ET
