T* (The system must support role-based access control for the roles Owners, Managers, Bakers, and) Tj
T* (Finance or Administration.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Version history must be available for shared documents. Deleted file recovery must be available) Tj
T* (for at least 30 days. File access, deletion events, and permission changes must be logged.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The transition period must support automated nightly synchronization between the on-premise file) Tj
T* (server and the cloud target until final cutover is completed.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (8. NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS) Tj
T* (------------------------------) Tj
T* (Files smaller than 25 MB must open within 5 seconds on a standard office internet connection.) Tj
T* (Upload of daily point-of-sale exports must complete within 2 minutes. Filename search across) Tj
T* (active folders must return results within 10 seconds.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The service must provide at least 99.9 percent availability for active business data. Critical) Tj
T* (folders must be replicated across at least two availability zones or an equivalent resilience) Tj
T* (model.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The solution must support at least 30 concurrent users without service degradation and must remain) Tj
T* (operable through a browser or synced folder client on standard staff workstations.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (9. SECURITY REQUIREMENTS) Tj
T* (------------------------) Tj
T* (All data must be encrypted in transit using TLS 1.2 or higher and encrypted at rest using AES-256) Tj
T* (or an equivalent modern standard.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Multi-factor authentication must be mandatory for owners, managers, and finance users. Public) Tj
T* (access to storage must be disabled by default.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Employee records, payroll documents, and HR-related files must be restricted to approved finance) Tj
T* (or HR roles only. The bakery accountant may only receive time-limited access to explicitly shared) Tj
T* (folders or files.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Audit logs must be retained for at least 12 months and must record file access, failed logins,) Tj
T* (permission changes, and deletion activity. Failed login thresholds must support monitoring and) Tj
T* (alerting.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (10. RETENTION AND COMPLIANCE REQUIREMENTS) Tj
T* (-----------------------------------------) Tj
T* (Financial records must be retained for 7 years. Supplier traceability, food safety, and sourcing) Tj
T* (documents must be retained for at least 5 years. Employee records must be retained according to) Tj
ET
