T* () Tj
T* (12. BACKUP AND DISASTER RECOVERY REQUIREMENTS) Tj
T* (---------------------------------------------) Tj
T* (Cloud data must be backed up daily. Backup retention must include daily backups for 30 days,) Tj
T* (monthly backups for 12 months, and annual backups for 7 years.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (At least one backup copy must be logically isolated from ordinary user deletion and) Tj
T* (ransomware-style tampering. Recovery Point Objective must be no greater than 24 hours and Recovery) Tj
T* (Time Objective must be no greater than 8 hours.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Restore capability must support single-file restore, folder-level restore, and full recovery of a) Tj
